➜跟着顺子哥咥“陕味儿”早点！你都吃了么？
http://www.sohu.com/a/436731450_355330	10340
<p><span>人间烟火</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">“赶早起来</span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">我饿得上气不接下气</span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">揣上票子穿上大衣</span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">出门打个的</span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">大街上</span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">到处都是一股香风辣雨</span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">要咥（吃）饭论美食</span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">还得数咱三秦大地</span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">......”</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px;"></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201207/47604ff9e37b4bf1ad0701223e2fe742.gif" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201207/7cf4a265f7da4e4fbd08f66c1f00f9dc.gif" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
